originalSql:
SELECT 
    p.p_name, 
    s.s_name AS supplier_name, 
    c.c_name AS customer_name, 
    o.o_orderdate, 
    SUM(l.l_extendedprice * (1 - l.l_discount)) AS total_revenue,
    COUNT(DISTINCT o.o_orderkey) AS total_orders,
    LEFT(p.p_comment, 10) AS short_comment,
    CONCAT('Supplier ', s.s_name, ' provides ', p.p_name) AS supplier_info
FROM 
    part p
JOIN 
    partsupp ps ON p.p_partkey = ps.ps_partkey
JOIN 
    supplier s ON ps.ps_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
JOIN 
    lineitem l ON p.p_partkey = l.l_partkey
JOIN 
    orders o ON l.l_orderkey = o.o_orderkey
JOIN 
    customer c ON o.o_custkey = c.c_custkey
WHERE 
    p.p_type LIKE '%BRASS%'
    AND o.o_orderdate >= DATE '1997-01-01'
    AND o.o_orderdate < DATE '1997-12-31'
GROUP BY 
    p.p_name, s.s_name, c.c_name, o.o_orderdate, p.p_comment
ORDER BY 
    total_revenue DESC, o.o_orderdate DESC
LIMIT 10

SELECT COALESCE("t4"."P_NAME", "t4"."P_NAME") AS "P_NAME", "t4"."SUPPLIER_NAME", "t4"."CUSTOMER_NAME", "t4"."O_ORDERDATE", "t4"."TOTAL_REVENUE", "t4"."TOTAL_ORDERS", "t4"."SHORT_COMMENT", "t4"."SUPPLIER_INFO", "t4"."o_orderdate" AS "o_orderdate_"
FROM (SELECT "part"."p_name" AS "P_NAME", MIN("supplier"."s_name") AS "SUPPLIER_NAME", MIN("customer"."c_name") AS "CUSTOMER_NAME", "orders"."o_orderdate" AS "O_ORDERDATE", SUM("s1"."l_extendedprice" * (1 - "s1"."l_discount")) AS "TOTAL_REVENUE", COUNT(DISTINCT "orders"."o_orderkey") AS "TOTAL_ORDERS", MIN(LEFT("part"."p_comment", 10)) AS "SHORT_COMMENT", MIN(CONCAT('Supplier ', "supplier"."s_name", ' provides ', "part"."p_name")) AS "SUPPLIER_INFO", "orders"."o_orderdate"
FROM "part"
INNER JOIN "partsupp" ON "part"."p_partkey" = "partsupp"."ps_partkey"
INNER JOIN "supplier" ON "partsupp"."ps_suppkey" = "supplier"."s_suppkey"
INNER JOIN "s1" ON "part"."p_partkey" = "s1"."l_partkey"
INNER JOIN "orders" ON "s1"."l_orderkey" = "orders"."o_orderkey"
INNER JOIN "customer" ON "orders"."o_custkey" = "customer"."c_custkey"
WHERE "part"."p_type" LIKE '%BRASS%' AND "orders"."o_orderdate" >= DATE '1997-01-01' AND "orders"."o_orderdate" < DATE '1997-12-31'
GROUP BY "part"."p_name", "supplier"."s_name", "customer"."c_name", "orders"."o_orderdate", "part"."p_comment"
ORDER BY 5 DESC NULLS FIRST, "orders"."o_orderdate" DESC NULLS FIRST
LIMIT 10) AS "t4"

SELECT COALESCE("o_orderkey", "o_orderkey") AS "o_orderkey", "o_custkey", "o_orderstatus", "o_totalprice", "o_orderdate", "o_orderpriority", "o_clerk", "o_shippriority", "o_comment"
FROM "orders"

INNER JOIN "partsupp" ON "part"."p_partkey" = "partsupp"."ps_partkey"
INNER JOIN "supplier" ON "partsupp"."ps_suppkey" = "supplier"."s_suppkey"
INNER JOIN "lineitem" ON "part"."p_partkey" = "lineitem"."l_partkey"
INNER JOIN "s1" ON "lineitem"."l_orderkey" = "s1"."o_orderkey"
INNER JOIN "customer" ON "s1"."o_custkey" = "customer"."c_custkey"

SELECT COALESCE("c_custkey", "c_custkey") AS "c_custkey", "c_name", "c_address", "c_nationkey", "c_phone", "c_acctbal", "c_mktsegment", "c_comment"
